data.description: Elevate your lifestyle in this irresistible gem! Step into luxury with designer upgrades that redefine sophistication. A breath of fresh air awaits with a new HVAC system and roof, accompanied by sleek new LVP flooring that seamlessly flows through the open layout. Transform your workdays in the chic office space and embrace the serenity of a large backyard, the perfect canvas for your outdoor dreams. Fully remodeled to perfection, this home exudes elegance with quartz countertops and a modern aesthetic. Immerse yourself in the timeless charm of 4 sides brick, and welcome guests with pride through a charming front porch. Convenience meets style with a spacious 2-car carport and an elongated driveway, providing ample parking. The professionally landscaped surroundings frame this haven, creating a visual masterpiece that complements the refined interiors. From the grandeur of the entrance to the tranquility of the backyard, every detail beckons you to call this home yours. Don't miss your chance Co seize the opportunity to own this blend of opulence and functionality that will have you saying, "We've gotta purchase this!"
